  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
          <p xml:id="KT71-kilavi">poruḷ kaṭaikkūṭṭiya neñciṟkut talaimakaṉ collic celavaḻuṅkiyatu.</p>
          <p xml:lang="en">HE dispensing with going, speaking to the heart that had accomplished wealth.</p>
          </div>



        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="KT71">
<l>                marunteṉiṉ maruntē vaippeṉiṉ vaippē</l>
<l>                yarumpiya cuṇaṅki ṉampakaṭ ṭiḷamulaip</l>
<l>                peruntō ṇuṇukiya nucuppiṟ</l>
<l>                kalkeḻu kāṉavar nalkuṟu makaḷē.</l>
             </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
          <l>“Remedy”, a nice remedy, “treasure”, a nice treasure:</l>   
          <l rend="indent">
            <choice>
                <seg>budding beauty-spots, pretty high young breasts,</seg>
                <seg>high young breasts with a number of budding beauty-spots<note place="foot">Here it is possible to split the sandhi in a different way, namely <term xml:lang="ta">cuṇaṅku iṉam pakaṭṭ’ iḷa mulai</term>.</note></seg>
            </choice>
          </l>
          <l rend="indent">slender waist, big shoulders,</l>
          <l>the innocent little daughter of the man from the stony forest.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
